      "writtenOn": "2026-06-09T21:05:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Long term I suspect some of the solution to this is to route the hwmon sampling into the kernel through iio, then blocking reads can be done without userspace even needing to initiate it, and values can be streamed out.  At least that\u0027s what the kernel folks recommended.",
      "revId": "9dd9bcdd4021fd59e23a75813efe95ac451d4f60",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
